## Risks & Mitigations

| Risk | Likelihood | Impact | Mitigation |
|------|------------|--------|------------|
| Warping artifacts (aliasing) | Medium | Medium | High-quality resampling, mipmapping |
| GPU memory exhaustion | Medium | High | Texture streaming, LOD, resource limits |
| Multi-output synchronization | Medium | High | Frame locking, v-sync, triple buffering |
| Calibration accuracy | Medium | Medium | Camera calibration, optimization algorithms |
| Shader compatibility | Low | Medium | Fallback software rendering, shader validation |

